BBQ Chicken Burger

25 min
$12.5
550 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Gluten (if buns are not gluten-free)Dairy (if cheese is used)

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinGluten-Free Options Available

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

EasyQuickComfort Food

Description

Juicy grilled chicken patties topped with smoky BBQ sauce, served in a toasted bun with fresh toppings.

Ingredients

  • ground chicken: 1 lb
  • burger buns: 4
  • bbq sauce: 1/2 cup
  • cheddar cheese slices: 4
  • lettuce leaves: 4
  • tomato slices: 1
  • onion slices: 1
  • olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • garlic powder: 1 tsp
